<h1 class="mb-4">About QueueLess</h1>

<p>
    QueueLess is a virtual queue management system designed to reduce physical waiting lines
    and improve customer experience.
</p>

<p>
    Instead of standing in crowded spaces, clients can track their position in a queue remotely,
    while businesses manage service flow efficiently.
</p>

